    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Assessment team accepted the package under the Minimal profile. Six of thirteen credibility factors remain not-assessed and all seven assessed factors show achieved levels below required levels for MRL-5. The intended-use scope is not defined in this package.",
